<br>
Such a useful little move, and also annoying when you are trying to smack someone who has a shield. &gt;.&lt;<br>
<br>
The fighting is kinda simplistic in ways, but you can fight different ways. For example, using a spear effectively, requires you to thrust. So you step in and out of the enemies attack jabbing them.<br>
When using a 1h sword, you try and chop or slash your enemy, keeping them slightly to your left so you can benefit from your shield, slowly circling them, waiting for their attack to swing your own.<br>
<br>
